author: PlayStation
description:
https://store.playstation.com/en-us/concept/10014503

Discover the secret of a forgotten war in Wings of Endless, a platforming Action-RPG with captivating pixel art that draws you in from start to finish.

Step into the role of Hariku, a brash bounty hunter who prides himself on being the best in the business. His life takes a dramatic turn when a seemingly routine mission spirals into an epic adventure — revealing the long-buried truths of an ancient war thought to have ended generations ago.

Joined by his enigmatic, talking owl companion Owly and a cast of unexpected allies, Hariku will journey through vast and varied landscapes — from arid deserts and misty marshlands to dense forests and icy snowfields. Every corner of this mesmerizing world is packed with secrets waiting to be uncovered.

Features:
- Dynamic combat: Control three unique heroes and switch between them in real-time.
- Huge and diverse world: Explore deserts, forests, snowfields, and more secrets.
- Gripping story
title: Wings of Endless - Launch Trailer | PS5 & PS4 Games

...Dreadful was the day when the sun vanished. The waters dried up, birds went quiet and The Dark Itself seeped unchecked into the Worktable. The night that followed would be long. As long as The Midnight Walk.

Embark on a journey in a mesmerizing and terrifying world sculpted from real life clay. Become The Burnt One, an enigmatic figure exploring a world steeped in wonder and darkness. Accompanied by Potboy, a lost lantern creature whose flame is key to survival, you must navigate twisted landscapes, outwit horrifying monsters, and uncover secrets lurking in the shadows.

The Midnight Walk is OUT NOW for PS5 & PS VR2!

author: PlayStation
description:
https://store.playstation.com/concept/10011452/

Have you ever had the feeling of being trapped in a nightmare with no way of getting out?
Do you want the craziest VR experience on PS VR2?

Take the time for a good horror movie and get ready... For anything!

As a famous adventurer would say, "in survival there are three immutable rules:
Survive, Survive, Survive. And occasionally Run!"

GET OUT! is a demanding game create by very tiny French indie Studio that pays homage to retro horror films.

"Get out!" is an original game derived from the "Very Bad Dreams" Franchise released on PSVR2
Playing a difficult patient locked in a strange mental asylum and experience a day like no other!
Exclusively developed for the PSVR2 with well-worked haptic capabilities (B-Haptics compatible).
Maybe the craziest VR Horror game ever...

#ps5 #psvr2 #psvr2games #getout 

Rated Mature
title: Get Out! - Gameplay Trailer | PS VR2 Games

author: PlayStation
description:
🌌 The Abandoned Planet – Available Now on #PS4 and #PS5! 🌌

When a wormhole tears open in space, an astronaut is hurled down and crashes on a distant planet. But where is she? Where are all the inhabitants of the planet? And how is she going to get back home?

Embark on a journey through a beautifully crafted pixel art world, inspired by classics like Myst and Riven, with a touch of 90s LucasArts charm.

🧩 Key Features:

- Over 300 unique areas to explore across 5 acts
- Classic point-and-click adventure gameplay
- Fully animated cutscenes and English voice acting
- Available in 12 languages, including Spanish, French, German, Japanese, and Russian

Experience a captivating story that blends nostalgia with modern design.

#ps5 #ps5games #ps4 #ps4games
title: The Abandoned Planet - Launch Trailer | PS5 & PS4 Games
